{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1677-08_133","@resp":"mercure","head":{"value":"[Epistre de M. de Ramboüillet]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Le Nouveau Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#1":{"value":", août 1677 (tome VI), p. 133-142","id":"/div/bibl/#1"},"note":{"@resp":"editor","#":{"value":"Il existe une autre édition parisienne, réalisée \"Suivant la Copie imprimée\" par la veuve O. de Varennes, dont la pagination diffère.","id":"/div/bibl/note/#"}},"#2":{"value":".","id":"/div/bibl/#2"}},"p":{"value":"Vous voulez bien, Madame, que de Montpellier je vous ramene à la Cour, &amp; que je vous fasse encor une fois part de l’Epistre qui fut envoyée par Monsieur de Ramboüillet à Monsieur le Prince de Marsillac apres les dernieres Conquestes du Roy. Il manquoit beaucoup de Vers à la Copie qui estoit dans ma derniere Lettre, vous le pourrez facilement connoistre en lisant celle-cy, où vous trouverez des agrémens qui n’estoient pas dans la premiere.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"label":{"#":[{"#":{"value":"A MONSEIGNEUR ","id":"/div/quote/label/#[0]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"LE PRINCE ","id":"/div/quote/label/#[2]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"DE MARSILLAC. ","id":"/div/quote/label/#[4]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"hi":{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Epistre.","id":"/div/quote/label/#[6]/hi/#"}}}]},"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au lieu de jeûner le Carème,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’estre avec un visage blème,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A faire vos Devotions,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vacquer à vos Stations ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout ce temps vous avez fait rage","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Parmy le sang &amp; le carnage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous n’avez malgré les hazards,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Songé qu’à forcer des Remparts,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous avez pris trois grandes Villes,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des Flamans les plus seurs aziles,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mesme vous avez fait périr","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ceux qui venoient les secourir.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puny leur audace insolente,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans une Bataille sanglante,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce que les plus grands Conquerans","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’auroient jamais fait en quatre ans.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Je ne sçay ce que le Saint Pere","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aura jugé de cette affaire,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais jamais chez les plus pieux","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Carème ne se passa mieux.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La prise de Valencienne,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est une action fort Chrestienne,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Violer quand on fut dedans,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sembloit estre du Droit des Gens.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le plus moderé, le plus sage","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Brusle alors, met tout au pillage.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vos Soldats mieux disciplinez,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[26]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par la seule gloire menez,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[27]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans une Place ainsi conquise,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Entrent comme dans une Eglise,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des Démons quand ils sont aux mains,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[30]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et quand ils sont Vainqueurs, des Saints.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[31]/#"}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/#"},"hi":[{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Loüis","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":", l’ame de ces merveilles","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[32]/hi[1]/#"}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui n’eurent jamais de pareilles,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[33]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Trouve maintenant à propos","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[34]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que les Corps prennent du repos.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[35]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il a bien voulu leur permettre","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[36]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelques sejours pour se remettre :","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Luy cependant fait mille tours,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’ame veille, elle agit toûjours,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et repasse sur toute chose,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[40]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pendant que le corps se repose.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[41]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais on dit que dans peu de temps","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[42]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous allez vous remettre aux champs.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[43]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où Diable allez-vous donc encore ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[44]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est-ce au Nord ? est-ce vers l’Aurore ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[45]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voulez-vous vous mettre sur l’eau ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[46]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et passer la Mer sans Vaisseau ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[47]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Dauphins de la Mer Baltique,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[48]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Baleines du Pole Arctique,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[49]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ma foy, vous n’aurez qu’à vouloir,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[50]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Viendront vos ordres recevoir,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[51]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et sur le Zelandois rivage,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[52]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous porter Canons &amp; Bagage.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[53]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ce n’est pas si grand’chose, enfin,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[54]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous avez bien passé le Rhin,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[55]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cette Barriere si terrible,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[56]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont le passage est si pénible,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[57]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que Rome, maistresse de tout,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[58]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A peine en vint jadis à bout,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[59]/#"}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ayant","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[60]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Loüis","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[60]/hi[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"à vostre teste,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[60]/hi[2]/#"}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous n’aurez rien qui vous arreste,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[61]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A ses armes tout réüssit,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[62]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout luy succede, tout luy rit.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[63]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" D’où vient que ceux de qui les veuës","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[64]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne sont pas assez étenduës,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[65]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Exaltent autant son bonheur,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[66]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que sa prudence &amp; sa valeur ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[67]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais quand on sçait estre severe","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[68]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans cesser toutefois de plaire,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[69]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lors qu’on sçait inspirer aux cœurs","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[70]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les desirs qui font les Vainqueurs,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[71]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le mépris des Parques cruelles,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[72]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que les Ministres fidelles","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[73]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont avec soin on a fait choix,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[74]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sont au dessus de leurs Emplois,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[75]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’avec justice on dispense","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[76]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et la peine &amp; la récompense,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[77]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’on sçait toutes choses prévoir,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[78]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A tous les accidens pourvoir,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[79]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que jamais on ne viole","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[80]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Don Sacré de sa parole,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[81]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avec ses talens merveilleux,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[82]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il est bien aisé d’estre heureux.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[83]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Cependant par trop entreprendre,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[84]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous pourriez plus perdre que pendre :","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[85]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il est vray qu’il faut que chacun","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[86]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Contribuë au bonheur commun.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[87]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On doit sacrifier sa vie","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[88]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A la gloire de sa Patrie.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[89]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ainsi, Seigneur, malgré les coups","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[90]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que le Rhin vit tomber sur vous,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[91]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tous les jours une ardeur nouvelle","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[92]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous fait exposer de plus belle.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[93]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais il est bon de regarder","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[94]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il ne faut pas tout hazarder,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[95]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que les Testes couronnées,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[96]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Doivent au moins estre épargnées.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[97]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Comment souffrez-vous que le Roy,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[98]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"(Je n’y pense point sans effroy)","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[99]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Soit à toute heure aux mousquetades,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[100]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Toûjours en butte aux cannonades,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[101]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous, Seigneur, qui soir &amp; matin","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[102]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le voyez nud comme la main ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[103]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous sçavez &amp; devez luy dire,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[104]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quoy que des Dieux son sang il tire,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[105]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Encore qu’il soit un Héros,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[106]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il est pourtant de chair &amp; d’os,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[107]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qu’il a besoin d’une Armure","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[108]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La mieux trempée &amp; la plus dure.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[109]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si son Frere n’en eut point mis,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[110]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il n’auroit pas des Ennemis","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[111]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans cette Bataille fameuse","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[112]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Eu la Victoire glorieuse,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[113]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et nous verrions dans la douleur","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[114]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Madame qui rit de bon cœur.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[115]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" L’Armure pourtant la meilleure","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[116]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’empesche pas qu’on n’y demeure,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[117]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Canon est encore plus fort,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[118]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Turenne a suby son effort,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[119]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et les Rois dont il est la foudre","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[120]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Peuvent en estre mis en poudre :","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[121]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ainsi vous devez tout oser","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[122]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour l’empescher de s’exposer ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[123]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui doit toûjours estre le Maistre,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[124]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En ce point ne doit jamais l’estre.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[125]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Le plus seur est de revenir,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[126]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rien n’a droit de vous retenir ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[127]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lors que des Beautez desolées","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[128]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sont par vostre absence accablées","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[129]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’ennuis &amp; de vives douleurs,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[130]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et leurs beaux yeux noyez de pleurs,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[131]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rien n’est préferable à ces Belles,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[132]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et la Gloire est moins belle qu’elles.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[133]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Leur Caresme est un peu trop long,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[134]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Leur Jubilé hors de saison.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[135]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pourtant quoy que la Bulle dise,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[136]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et tous les Canons de l’Eglise,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[137]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ils ne finiront que le jour","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[138]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’elles vous verront de retour.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[139]/#"}}]}}}}